Description: Limestone lintel of Rudjka: the block bears a text, cut in fair, sunk relief, giving the titles and dignities of Rudjka and the cartouche of Khafra. It is arranged in short vertical lines without dividers. No colour remains.
Curator's comments: Companion to lintel EA 1269 Bibliography: B. Porter & R. Moss, 'Topographical Bibliography of Ancient Egyptian Hieroglyphic Texts, Reliefs and Paintings' III (Oxford: Clarendon Press), 67; Part 2, 308.
Bibliographic references: James 1961 / Hieroglyphic texts from Egyptian stelae, etc. Part 1 (pl.8)
